data.description: Price Drop...Don't miss a fantastic opportunity to own this beautiful and well maintained 3 Bedroom, 3.5 bath home located in Wildwood, GA.  Only 15 minutes from Downtown Chattanooga, this lovely, move-in ready home with gorgeous views of Lookout Mountain and a picturesque rocking-chair front porch, features an open floor plan living room/kitchen with a good size eat in kitchen and an adorable breakfast bar. The  primary bedroom, located on the main floor, has loads of natural light and a full en suite bathroom. The second floor has 2 good size bedrooms and a shared full bath. Storage abounds in the floored attic areas on both sides of the bedrooms upstairs.  Looking for still more room? The basement is finished and has another full bathroom, a kitchenette and an office that could be used as a 4th bedroom, if desired.  The large backyard is ready to be used to entertain with a 20 foot concrete patio, a large deck and a screened in porch. With two long driveways, a two car garage and a large car-port, this property is ready to meet your family's parking, storage and housing needs. Contact me today to schedule your private showing of this unique  property.  Sellers are willing to give buyers a $2,000 flooring credit, with an acceptable offer.
